_sText:
Well, this map is a first version (hope not the last one) about the game Resident Evil (Remake from GameCube).
The maximum number of players is 20, 10 per equip. You start with: knife, grenade, usp and xm1014 (like the game, more or less).
The point of this map is to kill the other team, just that! Hope you like it!
